data.description: **At NO fault to the selller, buyer lost financing---This home is VA approved! Incredible opportunity to live that country life with this beautiful four bedroom, two bathroom home situated on an acre lot with a salt water pool and two car shop with power! This home was built in 2018 and it is the Clayton Homes Terminator, M175 (30'/76'). The owners made several upgrades including; huge gourmet farm kitchen, oversized refrigerator/freezer, oversized master bathroom and closet, added front porch with trex decking boards, in-ground 27' saltwater pool with concrete pad and slide, 1/4 acre fenced in animal pen, 24x24 shop with loft, 10x24 lean-to and 14x24 lean-to, massive living room with an extra "den" space that could act as a 5th bedroom option, man-cave or she-cave, and the crawl space was professionally wrapped with a moisture barrier. This is your opportunity to have it all out in the country! The only reason he sellers are selling is due to a job promotion. Conveniently located 25 minutes to Georgetown, 30 minutes to Conway, 35 min to Pawleys Island, 35 minutes to Lake City, and only 45 minutes to Florence! Schedule your viewing today before its too late!
